  <p>TL;DR: Add desired user to the sudoers group.</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code># switch to root
su - root
# add your name to group wheel, which is exactly sudoers group
usermod -aG wheel [USERNAME]
</code></pre></div></div>
